HEADWORD: Quandong
<hw>Quan"dong</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>The edible drupaceous fruit of an Australian tree (<spn>Fusanus
acuminatus</spn>) of the Sandalwood family; -- called also
<altname>quandang</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

